<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.5">
<l>cuṟṟum kuḻaltā ḻa<supplied>c</supplied>curi kaiyaṇaittu</l>
<l>maṟṟum palamā maṇipoṉ koṭaṇintu</l>
<l>muṟṟam pukuntu muṟuval ceytuniṉṟīr</l>
<l>eṟṟuk kituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having fastened a dagger and being arrayed</l>
<l>With many large jewels and gold, as well,</l>
<l>Entering the courtyard, as your curly hair hung [loose],</l>
<l rend="indent">you stood forming a smile;</l>
<l>For what? What is this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
